---
title: Double Grilled Chicken and Stone Fruit Salad with Basil Pesto
description: Enjoy all the flavours of summer in one amazing salad. Sweet stone fruit shine with savoury basil pesto, and tomatoes and tender spinach balance together to complement classic grilled chicken.

